.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: train, skateboard, car, quad-bike, boat
There 5 different types of food: banana, cabbage, cherry, peas, pomegranate
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: october, may, february, april, june
The people have 5 different hobbies: writing, baking, gardening, cooking, singing
5 different pets are kept: dog, fox, zebra, horse, snails

1. the person eating banana is the person driving the train
2. the person eating cabbage is the owner of the dog
3. the person who's hobby is writing is the person driving the skateboard
4. the person eating cherry is the person who's hobby is baking
5. the person driving the skateboard is to the right of the person driving the car
6. the person who's birthday is in october is the owner of the snails
7. the person who's birthday is in may is the person driving the quad-bike
8. the person who's hobby is gardening is in the middle
9. the person eating peas is on the far left
10. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the owner of the fox
11. the person who's birthday is in may is to the left or right of the owner of the horse
12. the person who's birthday is in april is the person who's hobby is cooking
13. the person eating pomegranate is the person who's birthday is in june
14. the person eating peas is to the left or right of the person driving the boat

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Food	|   peas	|    cherry	|     banana	|    cabbage	|    pomegranate	|
| Transport		|    quad-bike	|      boat	|      train	|     car	|     skateboard	|
| Hobby	|     singing	|      baking	|      gardening	| cooking	|     writing	|
| Birthday		|     may	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| april	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     fox	|     horse	|     snails	|     dog	|     zebra	|
